  "comments": "This coin have two main variant:<br />\r\n<span style=\"text-decoration:underline;\"><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">Type 1</span></span> The monogram is thick and both letter &quot;C&quot; and number &quot;5&quot; have a floral-like aspect. The extremities are curved and at bottom &quot;C&quot; and &quot;5&quot; are not intertwined.<br />\r\n<a href=\"https://en.numista.com/catalogue/images/618410702bf62.jpg\"><img src=\"https://en.numista.com/catalogue/images/miniatures/618410702bf62.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"200\" height=\"102\" /></a><br />\r\n<span style=\"text-decoration:underline;\"><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">Type 2</span></span> The monogram is thin and both letter &quot;C&quot; and number &quot;5&quot; have straight aspect. The extremities are curly and at bottom &quot;C&quot; and &quot;5&quot; are intertwined.<br />\r\n<a href=\"https://en.numista.com/catalogue/images/618410773908a.jpg\"><img src=\"https://en.numista.com/catalogue/images/miniatures/618410773908a.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"200\" height=\"96\" /></a>",
